        "description": {
            "value": "<p>While wearing this silver religious symbol of Erastil, you can cast the <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Disrupt Undead]{Disrupt Undead}</em> cantrip as an innate divine spell.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">3</span> command, Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> By touching a weapon you wield to the symbol and uttering a plea for Erastil's steadying hand, you grant that weapon the deadly d12 trait. Against undead, the weapon instead gains the fatal d12 trait. This blessing lasts for 1 minute, until you score a critical hit with the weapon, or until you aren't wielding the weapon.</p>"
